{"tid":1616001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蒙面法只係表面，暗中執行緊急法先係重點","createTime":"2019-10-03T09:14:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T09:28:06.000Z","uid":127735,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5aff73e57c5934bcc1e38d605ad1454fe60f7822","tid":1616001,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T09:14:40.000Z","msg":"對家想以緊急法強推蒙面法，令人專注起曬蒙面法到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係只要開左先例引用左緊急法<br />\n<br />\n短期佢就可以斷網；爆你門；凍結你資產；隨便捉你坐48小時<br />\n長期佢可以強行通過國歌法；辱警罪；國民教育......好多惡法即過<br />\n最大絕招係沿用大陸法律，即間接宣佈一國一制，香港即變香港市<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">重點係佢可以唔宣佈任何過左既惡法，但私底下就做齊曬！</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">同宜家暗地裡戒嚴一樣！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n唔好比蒙面法轉移視線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da4b1a3a1a166aba8702550b51fe69ed368899d3","tid":1616001,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T09:15:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1170edc2e3a783ca60a0263012ff0eef6d37da72","tid":1616001,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T09:15:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"58bb15ecbe8177ae16040cd949d5dc4a6f8c0240","tid":1616001,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T09:15:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"611b36ebc79f5d7d8e9652e787dae31311ab6c9c","tid":1616001,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T09:15:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d42ab0a370182d2bbe0d4186096e10e27470d731","tid":1616001,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T09:16:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f0d27d86b45ebd55f9c9f520f58ee988104deda","tid":1616001,"uid":127735,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T09:16:38.000Z","msg":"推爆上去等人清晰番個重點呀"},{"pid":"6cfc258301196922ac7c8c14aec5